For now, lets not consider manual blockades, as we block the option to add a manual blockade if we have our reservation there. Well change one thing regarding manual blockades iCals, itll be explained below. Most probably, the most common scenario to cover is Theres a reservation for the given dates in the given slot AND suddenly, an iCal blockade pops for the same slotdates. RoomAdminMisterPlan TBD Theres an iCal blockade for the given dates in the given slot AND suddenly,

a AlohaCamp reservation pops for the same slotdates this should be in theory not possible, right. When we spot such situation, do the following Send an email via Postmark to the Host Template ID List of properties to be added to the payload startDate nowego pniejszego elementu endDate pniejszego elementu nazwa obiektu nazwa miejsca slot numer rezerwacji nazwa iCala locale currentyear Send an event to Segment for analytics reason no support involve needed Lets do this onetime for all current Hosts to look for such occurrences to see if its a good approach and notify them if needed. Also, lets cover the case where, if theres an iCal blockade in the calendar, when a Host adds there a manual blockade First, we show him a warning modal so he needs to confirm that event If they add it, it does NOT overlap the iCal blockade, so its easier to spot

possible overbooking. Task ID 8694m1u2t Name CMS Deleting discounts added to the users wallet Description Context Often were experiencing troubles where a discount is added to one users account, while it should be added to an other one, as user has two accounts or the person that bought voucher for someone, added it to his account by mistake. As we dont want to gamble with transferring funds, we prefer to add a CMS user an option to delete a wallet cash event, so they can add a new one to the correct account. Task ACs In the CMS there is a new section under Discounts tab, where a CMS user can see all discounts applied to all accounts. We should put there all currently valid discounts codes from the past. Next to every row, theres a delete button, which deletes the given wallet cash from the users discounts list. Such action should
